"I have nothing to do with my father,
so I'll make good use of this money."

542
00:37:13,105 --> 00:37:14,482
Do you find that acceptable?

543
00:37:15,191 --> 00:37:17,902
His kids are living large now,

544
00:37:17,985 --> 00:37:19,695
but it's blood-stained money.

545
00:37:20,404 --> 00:37:22,448
"It was in the past,
but it was still wrong."

546
00:37:22,949 --> 00:37:24,700
If they had just said that,

547
00:37:24,784 --> 00:37:27,161
it would've been enough to ease our pain.

548
00:37:27,662 --> 00:37:29,455
Now that Park In-geun is dead,

549
00:37:29,997 --> 00:37:31,791
his kids should at least come out

550
00:37:31,874 --> 00:37:33,209
and ask for forgiveness.

551
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:37,505
Who else are we supposed to get
an apology from?

552
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:41,425
Did we deserve this? We did nothing wrong.

553
00:37:42,551 --> 00:37:45,846
Please, just apologize

554
00:37:45,930 --> 00:37:47,556
