555
00:37:48,099 --> 00:37:50,601
I really don't want to live like this.

556
00:38:02,071 --> 00:38:06,075
I came all the way from Busan
to Sydney, Australia.

557
00:38:09,203 --> 00:38:15,001
It's been nearly 40 years
since I last saw Park In-geun's family.

558
00:38:17,962 --> 00:38:22,717
NEW SOUTH WALES
AUSTRALIA

559
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:27,596
This is the driving range
and sports center

560
