563
00:38:45,990 --> 00:38:46,991
I mean,

564
00:38:47,616 --> 00:38:51,203
I can't believe
they're living such a happy life.

565
00:38:52,538 --> 00:38:55,207
That boat's got to be worth
several hundred million won.

566
00:38:57,752 --> 00:39:01,088
This property is currently valued
at over ten billion won.

567
00:39:04,133 --> 00:39:06,552
"Are you happy living it up

568
00:39:06,635 --> 00:39:10,431
with the money your father made
from killing people?"

569
00:39:11,182 --> 00:39:12,308
"Are you people

570
00:39:13,225 --> 00:39:16,937
willing to acknowledge it
and apologize at all?"

571
00:39:17,021 --> 00:39:18,731
That's what I want to ask them.

572
00:39:19,732 --> 00:39:20,941
Have you ever met Park In-geun?

573
