577
00:39:30,409 --> 00:39:35,956
He himself said that he was good
at managing people like that.

578
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:39,585
What kind of place
did Park In-geun say Brothers' Home was?

579
00:39:39,668 --> 00:39:41,295
A place of good deeds.

580
00:39:44,048 --> 00:39:45,841
They are extremely wealthy.

581
00:39:46,884 --> 00:39:50,721
It seems like the family was constantly
going back and forth to Korea,

582
00:39:50,805 --> 00:39:52,848
engaging in things like that.

583
00:39:52,932 --> 00:39:58,604
And every time Park Je-hui came back,
she always had new jewelry.

584
00:40:00,898 --> 00:40:03,234
They're a happy family,
thanks to their wealth.

585
00:40:10,825 --> 00:40:12,493
Wait, we should go that way.

586
00:40:22,545 --> 00:40:25,756
Hello, I'm Jo Seong-hyeon,
a producer at MBC.

587
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:26,966
IN-LAW OF PARK IN-GEUN

588
00:40:27,049 --> 00:40:28,759
-I'm from MBC in Korea.
-Okay.

589
00:40:28,843 --> 00:40:31,929
Are Ms. Park Je-hui
and Mr. Min Gyeong-u at home?

590
00:40:32,012 --> 00:40:33,222
They're in Korea now.

591
00:40:33,305 --> 00:40:34,682
-Are you his father?
-Yes.

592
00:40:34,765 --> 00:40:37,268
-I know what you're here to say.
-Right.

593
00:40:37,351 --> 00:40:39,854
-But stop doing that. You see…
-Yes?

594
00:40:39,937 --> 00:40:41,772
Why do you keep harassing people?

595
00:40:41,856 --> 00:40:43,566
Sir, let me tell you this.

596
00:40:43,649 --> 00:40:47,903
I'm a survivor of the Brothers' Home,
and while I was in there--

597
00:40:47,987 --> 00:40:50,281
-That has nothing to do with me.
-No, please wait.

598
00:40:50,364 --> 00:40:52,575
-Please hear me out.
-I'm not talking to you.

599
00:40:52,658 --> 00:40:55,161
We're here because Ms. Park Je-hui
is Park In-geun's--

600
00:40:55,244 --> 00:40:57,288
-No, just go.
-She's his daughter, right?

601
00:40:57,788 --> 00:40:58,873
Just leave.

602
00:40:58,956 --> 00:41:01,167
But, sir, do you at least admit

603
00:41:01,250 --> 00:41:04,795
