was purchased with Park In-geun's money?

604
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:08,591
No, that's not right.
You can request an investigation.

605
00:41:09,175 --> 00:41:11,677
Don't we have rights as well?

606
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:15,097
What wrong have
Park Je-hui and Min Gyeong-u done?

607
00:41:15,181 --> 00:41:18,267
I'm suing you, I swear.
There's a lawyer here too, okay?

608
00:41:18,350 --> 00:41:22,271
Park Je-hui's daughter is also on her way
to becoming a lawyer.

609
00:41:22,354 --> 00:41:23,522
You can't do this.

610
00:41:23,606 --> 00:41:26,192
Do you know how painful this is?

611
00:41:26,275 --> 00:41:28,569
I'm not just in pain.
I'm struggling to live.

612
00:41:28,652 --> 00:41:30,654
Well, I have no reason to talk to you.

613
00:41:30,738 --> 00:41:33,157
And, mister…
You say you're with a TV network?

614
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:34,658
But I'm the victim of--

615
00:41:34,742 --> 00:41:36,410
-You're taking it too far.
-Sir.

616
00:41:36,494 --> 00:41:39,538
What does it matter now
what Park In-geun did with his money?

617
00:41:39,622 --> 00:41:42,958
It does matter, sir.
Even the Australian government--

618
00:41:49,924 --> 00:41:53,594
HOME OF LIM YOUNG-SOON
FORMER BROTHERS' HOME PASTOR

619
00:41:53,677 --> 00:41:56,680
Hello, is Pastor Lim Young-soon here?

620
00:41:57,181 --> 00:41:58,182
No, he's not here.

621
00:41:58,265 --> 00:42:01,018
-We know he is inside.
-He's not.

622
00:42:01,101 --> 00:42:04,563
-Isn't this Pastor Lim Young-soon's home?
-No. It's not.

623
00:42:04,647 --> 00:42:05,564
-It's not?
-No.

624
00:42:07,983 --> 00:42:08,817
It isn't?

625
00:42:08,901 --> 00:42:11,612
So Pastor Lim Young-soon
doesn't live here?

626
00:42:11,695 --> 00:42:12,571
No, he doesn't.

627
00:42:19,078 --> 00:42:21,539
That makes no sense. Let's have a look.

628
00:42:47,314 --> 00:42:48,440
-Hello.
-Excuse me.

629
00:42:48,524 --> 00:42:50,985
Could you take a quick look at this?

630
00:42:51,068 --> 00:42:55,114
We checked with your next-door neighbor
and the register

631
00:42:55,197 --> 00:42:57,575
and confirmed that he lives in this house.

632
00:42:57,658 --> 00:42:59,076
-I see.
-Who is this person?

633
00:42:59,577 --> 00:43:01,161
Isn't he your father?

634
00:43:01,245 --> 00:43:02,413
Why are you here?

635
00:43:02,496 --> 00:43:03,998
We had questions for your father,

636
00:43:04,081 --> 00:43:07,001
so we tried to get in touch with him
from Korea as well.

637
00:43:07,084 --> 00:43:08,252
You can't come in here.

638
00:43:08,335 --> 00:43:10,421
-Okay, we won't go inside.
-You see, I…

639
00:43:10,504 --> 00:43:14,967
I really wanted to meet
Pastor Lim Young-soon.

640
00:43:15,050 --> 00:43:18,887
I was in the Brothers' Home
when I was young.

641
00:43:19,513 --> 00:43:22,057
Can you tell me who this guy is?

642
00:43:22,141 --> 00:43:23,517
It doesn't matter.

643
00:43:23,601 --> 00:43:26,353
I have some unrelated questions
I'd like to ask.

644
00:43:26,437 --> 00:43:28,480
Why did you say
Pastor Lim didn't live here?

645
00:43:28,564 --> 00:43:31,108
-I don't care.
-That's none of your business.

646
00:43:31,191 --> 00:43:33,193
-What's your name?
-No, hold on.

647
00:43:34,153 --> 00:43:36,280
Then where is he? We want to talk to him.

648
00:43:36,363 --> 00:43:37,865
It's none of your business!

649
00:43:37,948 --> 00:43:40,993
You find him, if you want to find him.
It's none of our business.

650
00:43:41,076 --> 00:43:43,829
Do you think
that he does not have any responsibility--

651
00:43:43,912 --> 00:43:45,914
What has he done, sorry? What has he done?

652
00:43:45,998 --> 00:43:48,083
-He is the victim.
-For what?

653
00:43:48,167 --> 00:43:49,835
Why is he the victim?

654
00:43:50,628 --> 00:43:52,171
I am a survivor of their abuse.

655
00:43:52,254 --> 00:43:54,214
My brother died there,

656
00:43:54,298 --> 00:43:56,508
and I was imprisoned
for five years as well.

657
00:43:56,592 --> 00:43:58,093
Look at this. See this?

658
00:43:59,553 --> 00:44:01,764
I was beaten so badly,
I lost all my teeth.

659
00:44:01,847 --> 00:44:03,307
How many years ago was that?

660
00:44:03,807 --> 00:44:05,351
It was, what, 50 years ago?

661
00:44:05,434 --> 00:44:07,227
You don't have to say anything.

662
00:44:07,728 --> 00:44:09,313
I was beaten when I was a kid.

663
00:44:09,396 --> 00:44:10,814
You don't have to say anything.

664
00:44:11,398 --> 00:44:12,483
I was beaten as a kid--

665
00:44:12,566 --> 00:44:14,818
Bye. We've asked you guys
to leave our property.

666
00:44:14,902 --> 00:44:16,737
Excuse me.

667
00:44:24,244 --> 00:44:25,079
Come on.

