00:44:28,874 --> 00:44:29,792
Come on.

669
00:44:31,001 --> 00:44:32,044
Let's go.

670
00:44:37,925 --> 00:44:39,593
Wow, seriously.

671
00:44:42,763 --> 00:44:44,056
This is infuriating.

672
00:45:16,255 --> 00:45:18,924
I was telling them
about the abuse I endured.

673
00:45:19,007 --> 00:45:22,428
I even took out my dentures to show them.

674
00:45:23,178 --> 00:45:26,640
As human beings,
they should at least hear me out,

675
00:45:27,141 --> 00:45:30,894
understand why it happened,
and know exactly what happened.

676
00:45:35,023 --> 00:45:39,445
Who can I even talk to about the sorrow
of my brother's wrongful death

677
00:45:40,028 --> 00:45:42,865
and the pain I've suffered my whole life?

678
00:45:43,907 --> 00:45:48,036
That's what makes me feel
so devastated and resentful.

679
00:45:51,540 --> 00:45:52,666
Goddamn it.

680
00:45:55,711 --> 00:45:56,712
Damn it.

681
00:46:25,949 --> 00:46:27,993
We can't enter that house anymore.

682
00:46:28,744 --> 00:46:31,038
-We'll just stay like this.
-Yes, let's wait.

683
00:46:43,217 --> 00:46:44,218
Excuse me.

684
00:46:44,301 --> 00:46:46,220
PARK IN-GEUN'S NIECE
PARK IN-GEUN'S NEPHEW-IN-LAW

