00:47:15,749 --> 00:47:17,042
Unbelievable.

694
00:47:17,125 --> 00:47:19,002
I was saying, "Excuse me,"

695
00:47:19,086 --> 00:47:21,129
and she looked at me while smiling.

696
00:47:21,630 --> 00:47:25,676
Seeing her drive away smiling
sent a chill down my spine.

697
00:47:25,759 --> 00:47:27,803
I got goosebumps all over my body.

698
00:47:31,098 --> 00:47:32,766
This is driving me nuts.

699
00:47:34,434 --> 00:47:38,730
BUSAN

