00:47:40,816 --> 00:47:42,651
I'm going to show you a picture.

701
00:47:42,734 --> 00:47:44,361
Please tell me who this is.

702
00:47:48,031 --> 00:47:48,866
I got it.

703
00:47:50,367 --> 00:47:51,702
Who is this?

704
00:47:51,785 --> 00:47:54,663
He's my second-oldest brother.

705
00:47:54,746 --> 00:47:57,457
His name is Park Du-seon.

706
00:48:09,511 --> 00:48:11,096
-Excuse me.
-Yes?

707
00:48:11,179 --> 00:48:13,891
Is Mr. Park Du-seon here?

708
00:48:14,474 --> 00:48:15,434
Who are you?

709
00:48:15,517 --> 00:48:18,395
I'm Jo Seong-hyeon, a producer at MBC.

710
00:48:18,478 --> 00:48:20,230
There's no one here by that name.

711
00:48:20,772 --> 00:48:22,482
-You're at the wrong place.
-Sorry?

712
00:48:22,566 --> 00:48:24,192
-No, I'm not him.
-Sorry?

713
00:48:24,276 --> 00:48:25,360
I'm not him.

714
00:48:25,444 --> 00:48:28,238
I don't know who Park Du-seon is.

715
00:48:29,364 --> 00:48:30,490
He's not here.

716
00:48:30,574 --> 00:48:31,909
-He's not?
-No.

717
00:48:32,409 --> 00:48:34,202
Who's Park In-geun?

718
00:48:34,286 --> 00:48:36,955
Mr. Park In-geun,
the director of Brothers' Home.

719
00:48:37,456 --> 00:48:39,958
-Where is this Brothers' Home?
-Jurye-dong.

720
00:48:42,169 --> 00:48:43,003
Unbelievable.

721
00:48:43,086 --> 00:48:46,173
-But weren't you the general secretary?
-No, I wasn't.

722
00:48:46,256 --> 00:48:49,384
Sir, the victims
just want to hear an apology.

723
00:48:49,468 --> 00:48:54,014
This person was partially paralyzed
while in the mental health facility.

724
00:48:54,097 --> 00:48:56,642
Don't you think these people are victims?

725
00:48:57,142 --> 00:48:59,478
I don't think so.

726
00:48:59,561 --> 00:49:02,564
They have nothing to do with me,
so just go.

727
00:49:03,649 --> 00:49:05,525
-Those people aren't victims?
